{"tid":1220362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］今次連都方向報立場被動搖","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T18:00:24.000Z","uid":20058,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39a7c9f109885670f2474aadeb8bb69415c93197","tid":1220362,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onccgongnedi/videos/400725627182693?s=100001313257075&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonccgongnedi%2Fvideos%2F400725627182693%3Fs%3D100001313257075%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=224e53bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onccgongnedi/videos/400725627182693?s=100001313257075&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n電話此起彼落的更新提示聲，陪伴着小編一整天，直至發貼這刻仍未完結。<br />\n<br />\n你或者會問，《港呢啲》作為一個十萬likes都未夠嘅網媒，平時啲片搞笑抽水為主，今日咁搞法會唔會做多咗呀？<br />\n<br />\n但經歷完呢一日你會發現，記錄對一個社會嚟講有幾重要。就算再小的平台，只要是有用心去記錄，就自然會有力量。<br />\n<br />\n香港人會永遠記得今日💪🏽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88267c325f00b1aaa043285ccac56d9ef830a0e3","tid":1220362,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44dd06e89cace61210e8c4e074370f3347a876f3","tid":1220362,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2311656ab66c61770d2b0ffd765ffb99bbe7e68","tid":1220362,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a463d4067a86aa7241d7d36df1ecdd782b7ee92c","tid":1220362,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re